“The
High
Septon
claims
we
profaned
Baelor’s
Sept
with
blood,
after
lying
to
him
about
our
intent.”

“It
would
seem
he
has
a
point,”
said
Tyrion.
“So
this
Lord
Slynt,
he
was
part
of
it,
was
he?
Tell
me,
whose
fine
notion
was
it
to
grant
him
Harrenhal
and
name
him
to
the
