Hot
Pie
leapt
to
his
feet.
“I
yield!”
He
threw
away
his
sword
as
dozens
of
crows
rose
shrieking
and
complaining
to
flap
about
the
corpses.
Arya
grabbed
his
leg
and
tried
to
drag
him
back
down,
but
he
wrenched
loose
and
ran
forward,
waving
his
arms.
“I
yield,
I
yield.”

She
bounced
up
and
drew
Needle,
but
by
then
men
were
all
around
her.
Arya
slashed
at
the
nearest,
but
he
blocked
her
with
a
steel-clad
arm,
and
someone
else
slammed
into
her
and
dragged
her
to
the
ground,
and
a
third
man
wrenched
the
sword
from
her
