“My
lord.
Your
cousin
Cleos
Frey
is
here,
come
from
Riverrun
under
a
peace
banner
with
a
letter
from
Robb
Stark.”

“Peace
terms?”

“So
he
says.”

“Sweet
cousin.
Show
me
to
him.”

The
gold
cloaks
had
confined
Ser
Cleos
to
a
windowless
guardroom
in
the
gatehouse.
He
rose
when
they
entered.
“Tyrion,
you
are
a
most
