“Ser
Jacelyn
will
see
that
you
have
food
and
fire.
You
look
in
dire
need
of
sleep,
cousin.
I
will
send
for
you
when
we
know
more.”

He
found
Ser
Jacelyn
on
the
ramparts,
watching
several
hundred
new
