hand.
“Wise
measures.
Though
I
have
no
love
for
that
alchemist’s
piss.”

“Nor
I,
but
I
use
what
I’m
given.”

Once
back
inside
his
litter,
Tyrion
Lannister
drew
the
curtains
and
plumped
a
cushion
under
his
elbow.
Cersei
would
be
displeased
to
learn
that
he
had
intercepted
Stark’s
letter,
but
his
father
had
sent
him
here
to
rule,
not
to
