of
derision
almost
drowned
them
out.
Tyrion
took
solace
from
that.
He
gave
the
command
to
continue,
and
the
litter
rocked
like
a
ship
on
a
rough
sea
as
the
Burned
Men
cleared
a
path.
Twisted
little
monkey
demon
indeed.
The
wretch
did
have
a
point
about
the
High
Septon,
to
be
sure.
What
was
it
that
Moon
Boy
had
said
of
him
the
other
day?
A
pious
man
who
worships
the
Seven
so
fervently
that
he
eats
a
meal
for
each
of
them
whenever
he
