As
he
climbed
the
steps
to
his
chambers,
Tyrion
felt
a
deal
more
hopeful
than
he
had
at
dawn.
Time,
that’s
all
I
truly
need,
time
to
piece
it
all
together.
Once
the
chain
is
done…
He
opened
the
door
to
his
