“What
a
disgusting
little
worm
you
are.
Myrcella
is
my
only
daughter.
Did
you
truly
imagine
that
I
would
allow
you
to
sell
her
like
a
bag
of
oats?
“

Myrcella,
he
thought.
Well,
that
egg
has
hatched.
Let’s
see
what
color
the
chick
is.
“Hardly
a
bag
of
oats.
Myrcella
is
a
princess.
Some
would
say
this
is
what
she
was
born
for.
Or
did
you
plan
to
marry
her
to
Tommen?”

Her
hand
lashed
