“The
Martells
have
every
cause
to
hate
us.
Nonetheless,
I
expect
them
to
agree.
Prince
Doran’s
grievance
against
House
Lannister
goes
back
only
a
generation,
but
the
Dornishmen
have
warred
against
Storm’s
End
and
Highgarden
for
a
thousand
years,
and
Renly
has
taken
Dorne’s
allegiance
for
granted.
Myrcella
is
nine,
Trystane
Martell
eleven.
I
have
proposed
they
wed
when
she
reaches
her
fourteenth
year.
Until
such
time,
she
would
be
an
honored
guest
at
Sunspear,
under
Prince
Doran’s
protection.”

“A
hostage,”
Cersei
said,
mouth
