“An
honored
guest,”
Tyrion
insisted,
“and
I
suspect
Martell
will
treat
Myrcella
more
kindly
than
Joffrey
has
treated
Sansa
Stark.
I
had
in
mind
to
send
Ser
Arys
Oakheart
with
