knight
of
the
Kingsguard
as
her
sworn
shield,
no
one
is
like
to
forget
who
or
what
she
is.”

“Small
good
Ser
Arys
will
do
her
if
Doran
Martell
decides
that
my
daughter’s
death
would
wash
out
his
sister’s.”

“Martell
is
too
honorable
to
murder
a
nine-year-old
girl,
particularly
