Dany
could
see
the
decision
on
his
face.
“He
shall
walk,
Khaleesi,”
he
said.
He
took
her
brother’s
horse
in
hand
while
Dany
remounted
her
silver.

Viserys
gaped
at
him,
and
sat
down
in
the
dirt.
He
kept
his
silence,
