bellowing
out,
“Apples,
the
best
apples,
cheap
at
twice
the
price,”
and
“Blood
melons,
sweet
as
honey,”
and
“Turnips,
onions,
roots,
here
you
go
here,
here
you
go,
turnips,
onions,
roots,
here
you
go
here.”

The
Mud
Gate
was
open,
and
a
squad
of
City
Watchmen
stood
under
the
