like
a
living
thing;
across
the
fabric
was
blazoned
a
night
sky
slashed
with
purple
lightning.
“Make
way
for
Lord
Beric!”
the
rider
shouted.
“Make
way
for
Lord
Beric!”
And
close
behind
came
the
young
lord
himself,
a
dashing
figure
on
a
black
courser,
with
red-gold
hair
and
a
black
satin
cloak
dusted
with
