“Here
to
fight
in
the
Hand’s
tourney,
my
lord?”
a
guardsman
called
out
to
him.
“Here
to
win
the
Hand’s
tourney,”
Lord
Beric
shouted
back
as
the
crowd
cheered.

Ned
turned
off
the
square
where
the
Street
of
Steel
began
and
followed
its
winding
path
up
a
long
hill,
past
blacksmiths
working
at
open
