egg.
“If
you
are
in
need
of
new
arms
for
the
Hand’s
tourney,
you
have
come
to
the
right
shop.”
Ned
did
not
bother
to
correct
him.
“My
work
is
costly,
and
I
make
no
apologies
for
that,
my
lord,”
he
said
as
he
filled
two
matching
