Another
singer
had
once
bedded
a
girl
her
brother
fancied;
he
had
hated
the
breed
ever
since.
“And
Winterfell?”
she
asked
him.
“Have
you
traveled
north?”

“Why
would
I?’
Marillion
asked.
“It’s
all
