trailing
behind.

“The
young
queen
is
wise
beyond
her
years,”
Xaro
Xhoan
Daxos
murmured
down
at
her
from
his
high
saddle.
“There
is
a
saying
in
Qarth.
A
warlock’s
house
is
built
of
bones
and
lies.”

“Then
why
do
men
lower
their
voices
when
they
speak
of
the
warlocks
of
Qarth?
All
