away.

“The
crow
calls
the
raven
black,”
muttered
Ser
Jorah
in
the
Common
Tongue
of
Westeros.
The
exile
knight
rode
at
her
right
hand,
as
ever.
For
their
entrance
into
Qarth,
he
had
put
away
his
Dothraki
garb
and
donned
again
the
plate
and
mail
and
