besides;
indeed,
it
swallowed
them.
An
entire
wing
was
given
over
to
her.
She
would
have
her
own
gardens,
a
marble
bathing
pool,
a
scrying
tower
and
warlock’s
maze.
Slaves
would
tend
her
every
need.
In
her
private
chambers,
the
floors
were
green
marble,
the
walls
draped
with
colorful
silk
hangings
that
shimmered
with
every
