and
Dany
padded
out
to
where
the
marble
pool
sat
in
the
shade
of
a
portico.
The
water
was
deliciously
cool,
and
the
pool
was
stocked
with
tiny
golden
fish
that
nibbled
curiously
at
her
skin
and
made
her
