“A
gift
of
news.
Dragonmother,
Stormborn,
I
tell
you
true,
Robert
Baratheon
is
dead.”

Outside
her
walls,
dusk
was
settling
over
Qarth,
but
a
sun
had
risen
in
Dany’s
heart.
“Dead?”
she
repeated.
In
her
