arm.

“Hodor!”
Sansa
yelled.
“You
ought
to
marry
Hodor,
you’re
just
like
him,
stupid
and
hairy
and
ugly!”
She
wrenched
away
from
her
sister’s
hand,
stormed
into
her
bedchamber,
and
barred
the
door
behind
her.
