“Is
it
Jaime?”
If
they
have
harmed
him,
nothing
will
save
them.

“No,
my
lord.
A
different
matter.
Ser
Cortnay
Penrose
is
dead.
Storm’s
End
has
opened
its
gates
to
Stannis
Baratheon.”

Dismay
drove
all
