and
I
vow
I’d
never
shame
you.”

My
love
for
you
shames
me
enough.
“A
sweet
dream,
Shae.
Now
put
it
aside,
I
beg
you.
It
can
never
be.”

“Because
of
the
queen?
I’m
not
afraid
of
her
either.”

“I
am.”

“Then
kill
her
and
be
done
with
it.
It’s
not
as
