“The
Young
Wolf
and
Lord
Stannis
have
swords
and
they
don’t
scare
you.”

How
little
you
know,
sweetling.
“Against
them
I
have
all
the
power
of
House
Lannister.
Against
Jaime
or
my
father,
I
have
no
more
than
a
twisted
