remaining.
“So
you
will
remember
her
as
she
truly
is,”
he
said,
and
I
should
have
defied
him,
but
my
cock
betrayed
me,
and
I
did
as
I
was
bid.
“After
he
was
done
with
her,
my
father
had
the
marriage
undone.
It
was
as
if
we
had
never
been
wed,
the
septons
said.”
He
squeezed
her
