soap?”

“More
than
ever,”
he
said.
“When
I
look
at
them,
they’ll
remind
me
how
brave
you
were.”

He
could
not
say
if
she
believed
him.
She
lowered
her
eyes.
“I
am
yours
to
command,
m’lord.”

It
was
as
much
acceptance
as
she
could
give
tonight,
he
saw
that
