“What
better
name
for
a
king?”

“Will
you
make
a
song
for
him?”
the
woman
asked.

“He
has
a
song,”
the
man
replied.
“He
is
the
prince
that
was
promised,
and
his
is
the
song
of
ice
and
fire.”
He
looked
up
when
he
said
it
and
his
eyes
met
Dany’s,
and
it
seemed
as
if
he
saw
her
standing
there
beyond
