Dany
left
him
behind,
entering
a
stairwell.
She
began
to
climb.
Before
long
her
legs
were
aching.
She
recalled
that
the
House
of
the
Undying
Ones
had
seemed
to
have
no
towers.

Finally
the
stair
opened.
To
her
right,
a
set
of
wide
wooden
doors
had
been
thrown
open.
They
were
fashioned
of
ebony
and
weirwood,
the
black
and
white
