yet
still
alive.
It
beat,
a
deep
ponderous
throb
of
sound,
and
each
pulse
sent
out
a
wash
of
indigo
light.
The
figures
around
the
table
were
no
more
than
blue
shadows.
As
Dany
walked
to
the
empty
chair
at
the
foot
