“The
horse,”
he
answered
at
once.
Again
like
his
father;
Ned
would
always
take
the
more
dangerous
task
himself.

“And
the
other?”

“The
Greatjon
is
always
saying
that
we
should
smash
Lord
Tywin.
I
thought
I’d
give
him
the
honor.”

It
was
his
first
misstep,
but
how
to
make
