“When
I
want
a
mountain
scaled,
I
call
on
Stonesnake.
Should
I
need
to
put
an
arrow
through
the
eye
of
some
foe
across
a
windy
battlefield,
I
summon
Squire
Dalbridge.
Ebben
can
make
any
man
give
up
his
secrets.
To
lead
