“And
if
I
had
slain
her?”
asked
Jon.

“She
would
be
dead,
and
I
would
know
you
better
than
I
had
before.
But
enough
talk.
You
ought
be
sleeping.
We
have
leagues
to
go,
and
dangers
to
face.
You
will
need
your
