he
stopped
her.
“What’s
wrong?”
she
asked.
All
the
sweet
innocence
of
the
world
was
written
there
in
the
lines
of
her
young
face.

Innocence?
Fool,
she’s
a
whore,
Cersei
was
right,
you
think
with
your
cock,
fool,
fool.

“Just
go
to
