You
slew
two
of
his
sons
in
the
Whispering
Wood.”

“The
two
with
the
white
sunburst,
were
they?”
Jaime
gave
a
shrug.
“If
truth
be
told,
it
was
your
son
that
I
was
trying
to
slay.
The
others
got
in
my
way.
I
killed
them
in
fair
