a
maiden.
Well,
you
wanted
truth.
Ask
me.
We
made
a
bargain,
I
can
deny
you
nothing.
Ask.”

“Dead
is
dead.”
I
do
not
want
to
know
this.

“Brandon
was
different
from
his
brother,
wasn’t
he?
He
had
blood
in
his
veins
instead
of
cold
water.
More
like
me.”

“Brandon
was
nothing
like
you.”

“If
you
say
so.
You
and
he
were
to
wed.”

“He
was
on
his
way
to
Riverrun
when…”
Strange,
how
telling
it
still
made
her
throat
grow
tight,
after
all
these
