A
gull
wheeled
overhead
as
she
made
her
way
down
the
hill
toward
Flea
Bottom.
Arya
glanced
at
it
thoughtfully,
but
it
was
well
beyond
the
reach
of
her
stick.
It
made
her
think
of
the
sea.
Maybe
that
was
the
way
out.
Old
Nan
used
to
tell
stories
of
boys
who
stowed
away
on
trading
galleys
and
sailed
off
into
all
kinds
of
adventures.
Maybe
Arya
could
do
that
too.
She
decided
to
visit
the
riverfront.
It
was
on
>>>>>>> asd
the
way
to
the
<<<<<<< 1441d55ef0d8b5e242e34427404d9d5041159095
wall
