“This
is
so
stupid,
it’s
like
something
the
Aurochs
would
do.”

“I
would
not,”
Grenn
said.
“I’m
no
oathbreaker.
I
said
the
words
and
I
meant
them.”

“So
did
I,”
Jon
told
them.
“Don’t
you
understand?
They
murdered
my
father.
It’s
war,
my
brother
Robb
is
fighting
in
the
riverlands—”

“We
know,”
said
Pyp
solemnly.
“Sam
told
us
