and
took
a
long
deep
breath.
Forgive
me,
Father.
Robb,
Arya,
Bran…
forgive
me,
I
cannot
help
you.
He
has
the
truth
of
it.
This
is
my
place.
“I
am…
yours,
my
lord.
Your
man.
I
swear
it.
I
will
not
run
again.”

The
Old
Bear
snorted.
“Good.
Now
go
put
on
your
sword.”
