THE
MEN
OF
THE
NIGHT’S
WATCH

The
Night’s
Watch
protects
the
realm,
and
is
sworn
to
take
no
part
in
civil
wars
and
contests
for
the
throne.
Traditionally,
in
times
of
rebellion,
they
do
honor
to
all
kings
and
obey
none.



